node.text: Who’s excited to have organic footies back? We sure are! They are one of the favorite items here at Mebie Baby. #mebiebaby

node.text: Organic cotton is here! We’re so excited for the new color, navy! Also, sizing in the footies now goes up to 3T! Grip on the feet from size 6-12 to 3T. Yay!! #mebiebaby

node.text: Did your babies like to be swaddled or arms free? My two did not love being swaddled. That was before Mebie Baby stretch swaddles, so I hope baby on the way will enjoy it. 🥰 #mebiebaby

node.text: Who’s ready for an organic cotton restock? We will be restocking most colors of gowns and footies, the release will be Thursday at 8:00 am MST! The colors we have are, dusty rose, vanilla, oatmeal, mustard, plum, green and a navy! #mebiebaby
